Package com.intuit.datum_ipsum.model

Class Sequence

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intuit.datum_ipsum.model.Sequence
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Sequence
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Top level object used to represent a set of strings. A sequence is comprised of an ordered list of wheels and also tracks various counts of the strings. A sequence also contains a random number generator, used for generating new strings from the sequence.
